high_descs: Walk up to the end table with the newspaper on it.
Pick up the newspaper.
Turn right and take four steps, turn right again and walk over and stand in front of the couch.
Put the newspaper, standing upright, on the right cushion of the couch; on the top left side of the cushion.
Turn left and walk over to the chair and stand in front of it.
Pick up the newspaper from the chair cushion.
Turn right and walk over to stand in front of the couch.
Put the newspaper, standing upright, in between the two cushions.
anns.task_desc: Place two newspapers on the couch, standing vertically.

high_descs: Move forward to the table on the left of the couch.
Pick up the newspaper from the table.
Turn around and move to the loveseat on the other side of the room.
Set the newspaper down on the right cushion.
Turn left and move to the chair.
Pick up the newspaper from the chair.
Turn around and move back to the loveseat on your left.
Set down the newspaper on the loveseat to the right of the first newspaper.
anns.task_desc: Put two newspapers on the loveseat.
